Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Main gets dragged into a dubious plot}Myne bị kéo vào một âm mưu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{and lets her mana go berserk.}và khiến ma lực mất kiểm soát.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.30,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Lord Sylvester, you liar.}Ngài Sylvester nói dối,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.77,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You promised to protect me.}đã hứa bảo vệ mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:17.28,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Main, where did you get that?}Myne, con có thứ đó ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.07,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He gave it to me after he went hunting.}Con nhận được lúc đi săn với ngài Sylvester.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.91,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He said it was a protective charm.}Nghe nói đây là bùa hộ mệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:23.69,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.41,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{That is a powerful protective charm indeed.}Đó là một lá bùa cực mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:29.28,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What do you mean by that?}Là sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:30.65,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{That's only...}Con...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.42,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{if you are prepared to become \NSylvester's daughter.}sẽ trở thành con gái nuôi của Sylvester.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.62,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{If that is how to save everyone...}Nếu có thể cứu mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.68,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Then I will proceed.}Thì con sẽ làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.47,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{If you've made up your mind...}Nếu con đã quyết tâm rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:49.80,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main, pray to the wind and protect them.}Myne, hãy cầu xin nữ thần gió bảo vệ họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.75,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Protect them from my mana.}Khỏi ma lực của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.02,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Everyone here... My family...}Mọi người... gia đình mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:02.71,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm going to protect them!}Mình sẽ bảo vệ họ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.79,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Lord Karstedt!}Ngài Karstedt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.86,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Sorry to keep you waiting, Main.}Xin lỗi đã để nhóc chờ nhé, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.89,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Lord Sylvester!}Ngài Sylvester!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.30,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Ferdinand, that's enough. Well done.}Ferdinard, đủ rồi. Làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:29.30,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Main, you may put down your shield as well.}Myne, nhóc cũng giải trừ vòng bảo vệ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:38.07,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Wait. Is the head priest's\Nrank lower than his?}Ủa? Mình tưởng linh mục trưởng cấp cao hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:42.07,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Oh, Sylvester! You came at the perfect time!}Ồ, Sylvester! Đến đúng lúc lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.26,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{What is this mess?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:46.04,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Let's hear what's going on...}Để ta nghe thử xem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.91,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Uncle.}Chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:49.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.41,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{And who's that supposed to be?}Kẻ nào thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.12,Default,Karstedt,0,0,0,,{This is Aub Ehrenfest.}Đây là Aub Ehrenfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.50,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{H-He couldn't be...}K-Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.01,Default,Main,0,0,0,,Aub... Ehrenfest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.96,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Main, that's the lord.}Myne, là ngài lãnh chúa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.62,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The lord?}Lãnh chúa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:09.47,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.68,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:17.20,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.50,Title,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1700,1)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.01,Title2,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,900)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:58.00,Ep Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{Chapter Thirty-Six\NBlessing}Chương 36: Ban phước
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.25,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Otto, Lutz, what happened?}Otto, Lutz, có chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:06.20,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{And so Mister Gunther and \NMain went to the cathedral.}Và chú Gunther đi cùng Myne đến nhà thờ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.74,Default,Otto,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, Main \Nsaid something strange.}Nghĩ lại thì Myne nói gì đó lạ lắm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.78,Default,Otto,0,0,0,,{She said we needed to call for \Nhelp in that situation.}con bé nói sẽ kêu người giúp trong tình hình này.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.14,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{And?}Và?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.89,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{She used her blood seal on the \Nblack stone hanging from her neck.}Cậu ấy dùng máu nhỏ lên hòn đá đen đeo trên cổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.40,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Damn it! It's too early for that!}Chết tiệt! Sớm quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.41,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.31,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,Myne sẽ ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:33.21,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{Main... will be okay.}Myne... sẽ ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.05,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You may look up.}Ngẩng đầu lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.67,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Is there anything you'd like \Nto say, Count Bindewald?}Có gì để nói không, ngài bá tước Bindewald?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:56.17,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{I'd like you to punish that commoner!}Tôi muốn xử phạt con thường dân kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.19,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Commoner, you say?}Thường dân?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.20,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{This little brat named Main!}Con nhãi tên Myne này!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.72,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{She used her magic against a noble!}Nó dám sử dụng ma thuật lên quý tộc!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.04,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{She is truly a dangerous, \Ntreacherous little commoner!}Một con nhãi thường dân nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.01,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You seem to have the wrong \Nidea about something.}Hình như ngươi hiểu lầm gì thì phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.86,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,Cô bé ngươi gọi là thường dân
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.55,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{is my adopted daughter.}là con gái nuôi của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.03,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{Absurd!}Vớ vẩn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.13,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Main.}Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.50,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{The proof...}Bằng chứng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.80,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{is right here.}đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.92,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{And what's that?}Đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.31,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{A magic item that finalizes a contract \Nonce a blood seal is used.}Vật phẩm ma thuật sử dụng máu để làm khế ước.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.57,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Do you understand now?\N Main is already my daughter.}Ngươi đã hiểu chưa? Myne là con gái nuôi của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:46.65,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Which would mean that you attacked a \Nrelative of the lord of this domain.}Tức là ngươi đã tấn công vào gia quyến của lãnh chúa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.83,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{No...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:54.33,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Count Bindewald, you not only \Nentered this city illegally,}Bá tước Bindlewald, ngươi không \Nchỉ vào lãnh địa không xin phép,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.33,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{but you attacked its lord's daughter \Nas well as her knight bodyguard.}mà còn tấn công con gái của lãnh chúa cùng kị sĩ hộ vệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.18,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You will be taken into custody. Seize him!}Bắt lấy hắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:12.04,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I will sentence you once all of \Nyour crimes have become clear.}Ta sẽ kết án sau khi xem xét tội trạng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.52,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Uncle.}Chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.06,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,Sylvester!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.83,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I knew none of this!}Ta không biết gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.72,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{This was all devised by Count Bindewald!}Tất cả là do bá tước Bindewald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.56,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I just did what I was told!}Ta chỉ làm theo những gì hắn nói!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.80,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You're making excuses?}Chối tội sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.06,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{That's rather unsightly, Uncle.}Thật thảm hại, chú à.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.25,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{It's the truth! You have \Nto believe me, Sylvester!}Là sự thật! Cháu phải tin ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.83,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I didn't do anything wrong!}Ta không làm gì sai cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.59,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Tell that cur to untie me at once!}Mau kêu tên khốn kia cởi trói cho ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.24,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{And now calling him a cur...}Tên khốn à...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.59,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{My little brother.}Em trai của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.84,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Little brother?}Em trai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:50.46,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{These two are brothers?}Hai người họ là anh em hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:55.38,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Who cares about a younger brother \Nwho has some whore as a mother?}Ai thèm quan tâm tới thằng em\N có mẹ là con điếm rách nào đó chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.84,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I ask that you refrain from insults.}Cháu yêu cầu chú không nên nói thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:04.36,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Though our mothers are different, \Nhe is still my precious little brother.}Tuy khác mẹ nhưng vẫn là em trai yêu quý của cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.94,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Don't let him fool you, Sylvester!}Đừng để nó lừa, Sylvester!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.12,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I'm sure he's the one who coaxed \Nyou into adopting Main, as well!}Nó đã dụ dỗ cháu nhận nuôi Myne chứ gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:15.11,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Nullify this adoption at once! \NThis is my warning as your uncle!}Mau huỷ bỏ việc đó ngay! Ta cảnh báo cháu đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:22.25,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{You are my precious little nephew! \NI wish you no misfortune!}Cháu là cháu trai yêu quý của ta! \NTa không muốn cháu gặp xui xẻo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.73,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Sylvester! I'm...}Sylvester! Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.51,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I'm saying this for your own good!}Ta chỉ vì cháu thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.88,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{And now crocodile tears...}Giờ thì khóc nhè...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.77,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I'm worried about you from \Nthe bottom of my heart!}Ta lo lắng cho cháu từ tận con tim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:39.63,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{As the lord, I will cast aside any \Nattachment I have for you as a relative,}Với tư cách lãnh chúa, cháu sẽ huỷ bỏ mối quan hệ với chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.26,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{and place judgment upon you.}Và phán xét chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.67,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Uncle, you went too far.}Chú đã đi quá xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.12,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I cannot turn a blind eye any longer.}Cháu không thể làm ngơ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.30,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{This commotion you caused}Vụ việc lần này
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.62,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{is worthy of the death penalty.}xứng đáng bị tử hình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.88,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.87,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{That goes for all of your accomplices, too.}Áp dụng cho tất cả những kẻ theo chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.74,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Take him away!}Đưa ông ta đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.63,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,Sylvester!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.35,Default,Delia,0,0,0,,{Lady Main, please take care of Dirk for me.}Tiểu thư Myne, hãy chăm sóc Dirk thay tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.11,Default,Main,0,0,0,,Delia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.51,Flashback,Delia,0,0,0,,{Why weren't you there to help me?}Tại sao cô không ở đó giúp tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.78,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Lord Sylvester, I have \Na favor to ask of you.}Ngài Sylvester, con có điều muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.40,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Name it.}Nói đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.27,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Would you consider sparing Delia?}Ngài có thể tha thứ cho Delia không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.60,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{And why is that?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.49,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Delia was only deceived.}Delia chỉ là bị lợi dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.40,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I don't believe she had any \Ninvolvement in their evil deeds.}Con không tin cậu ấy có ác ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.39,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Be that as it may, if she was \Ninvolved in this incident,}Dù là thế, con bé đã can dự vào vụ việc này,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.53,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{she must face some punishment.}nên cần phải bị phạt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:48.12,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{As the daughter of the lord, \Nyou may decide her punishment.}Vậy con hãy quyết định hình phạt đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.67,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Let's see what you decide.}Ta sẽ xem xét.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.18,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{For her punishment, I order that \NDelia return to the orphanage.}Hình phạt là Delia sẽ phải quay lại trại mồ côi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.39,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You will be no one's attendant.}Và sẽ không thể trở thành phụ việc của ai nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You will spend the rest of your life taking \Ncare of Dirk and all of the other orphans.}Dành phần đời còn lại chăm sóc Dirk \Nvà những đứa trẻ khác ở trại mồ côi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.31,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{That is your duty from now on, Delia.}Đó là nhiệm vụ của Delia từ bây giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.56,Default,Delia,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn tiểu thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.07,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Are you Main's biological father?}Ngươi là cha ruột của Myne à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.32,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Yes. My name is Gunther.}Vâng, tôi tên là Gunther.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.33,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{We will now finalize this \Ncontract for the adoption.}Giờ chúng ta sẽ hoàn tất thủ tục nhận nuôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.24,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Go summon your family.}Hãy gọi gia đình đến đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.60,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Yes, sire.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.59,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.99,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Dad, what happened to your arm?}Ba, vết thương đó là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.23,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{It's no big deal. Main's \Nwaiting for us. Let's go.}Không có gì đâu. Myne đang chờ chúng ta. Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.95,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{Mister Gunther, where's Main?}Chú Gunther, Myne đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.55,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{I promise I'll explain \Neverything to you later.}Chú sẽ giải thích rõ ràng lại sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.69,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Just wait for me.}Chờ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.89,Default,Arno,0,0,0,,{Perhaps you should get some rest.}Cậu nên nghỉ ngơi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.19,Default,Fran,0,0,0,,{I'm fine.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.96,Default,Arno,0,0,0,,{You're so inflexible, Fran.}Fran không dẻo dai lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.60,Default,Fran,0,0,0,,{I could say the same about you, Arno.}Cậu cũng thế còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:14.47,Default,Fran,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you tell me that the head \Npriest was in his hidden room?}Sao không nói tớ nghe linh mục trưởng đang ở phòng bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.78,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{You may take your leave.}Đủ rồi, lui ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.36,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Main, let's talk about your future.}Myne, nói chuyện về tương lai nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.95,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Am I going to become Lord \NKarstedt's daughter first}Đầu tiên con sẽ trở thành con gái ngài Karstedt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:33.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{and then become yours, Lord Sylvester?}sau đó trở thành con gái nuôi của ngài?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.10,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Well, a former commoner girl}Một cô bé thường dân
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:44.32,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{being adopted is quite different \Nfrom a noble girl being adopted.}được nhận làm con nuôi khác hoàn toàn \Nvới con quý tộc được nhận nuôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:50.49,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You are the beloved daughter of Lord \NKarstedt's third wife, who perished.}Con là con gái của người vợ thứ 3 đã qua đời\N mà ngài Karstedt vô cùng yêu quý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.59,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Talk about illegally messing with \Nsomeone's family register.}Cứ như đang hợp pháp hoá vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.62,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{As for the Gilberta Company...}Về thương hội Gilberta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.76,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I considered having them close up shop...}Ta cân nhắc đóng cửa hàng của họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.76,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.78,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{But they are absolutely necessary \Nto keep the printing business}Nhưng họ có vẻ cần thiết cho công việc in ấn của con
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.15,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{as one of this city's industries.}cũng như nền công nghiệp thành phố này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.01,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I will let you continue your \Nrelationship with them.}Ta sẽ để yên như trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.14,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.89,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Regarding your birth family...}Về gia đình con...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.65,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{You are going to become \Nthe daughter of the lord.}Con sẽ trở thành con gái lãnh chúa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.04,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Your name will change.}Tên con sẽ thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.04,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Seeing your family...}Gặp gia đình...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.03,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{will be prohibited from now on.}sẽ bị cấm từ bây giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.96,Eyecatch_an4,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:39.05,Eyecatch_an6,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.50,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Come in.}Vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.17,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.65,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Tuuli!}Turi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.15,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Main, are you okay?}Myne, con ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:55.38,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{The look on Dad's face was scary when\Nhe came to get me, and he was injured.}Mặt ba đáng sợ với thêm vết thương nên chị lo lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:58.73,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{And now even Mom and Kamil\Nhave to come to the cathedral...}Và giờ thì cả mẹ lẫn Kamil cũng bị gọi lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:03.92,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{I was really scared that something \Nmight've happened to you.}Chị sợ có chuyện gì xảy ra với em quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.28,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad you're okay!}Thật may khi em vẫn an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.17,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Tuuli, you need to bow, as well.}Turi, mau cúi xuống.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.11,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:22.61,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{In order to conclude this\Nincident without further issue,}Để kết thúc vụ việc này trong hoà bình,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.17,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{it has been decided that \NMain will be adopted by me.}ta sẽ nhận nuôi Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.68,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{The commoner Main is now dead.}Myne thường dân đã chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.69,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.69,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Is this my fault?}Là lỗi tại chị sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.81,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{It's not.}Không phải đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.81,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{But then why...}Vậy tại sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.32,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Dad must've known.}Ba hẳn phải biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:46.27,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{All of you are obstacles to Main\Nbecoming your lord's daughter.}Tất cả các ngươi đều là trở ngại\N khi Myne trở thành con gái lãnh chúa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:48.95,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{I thought of having all of \Nyou dealt with, too.}Ta đã nghĩ đến việc xử lý các ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.80,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{But then Main would probably go berserk,}Nhưng làm thế Myne sẽ mất kiểm soát,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.21,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{so I'm allowing all of you to live.}nên ta sẽ cho phép các ngươi sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.75,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{But I cannot allow you to see \Nher as her family any longer.}Nhưng ta không cho phép các ngươi\N xem con bé như gia đình nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.35,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Once you sign the contract, I will \Nallow you to continue seeing her.}Một khi kí vào khế ước này,\N ta sẽ cho phép các ngươi gặp con bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.02,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Main, read it to them.}Myne, đọc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.76,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{"You are to announce to everyone \Naround you that Main has died."}"Phải thông báo Myne đã chết với mọi người".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.08,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{"If you are ever to encounter \NMain from now on,}"Nếu gặp Myne từ bây giờ,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.65,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{you will not claim to be her family."}các ngươi không được xưng là gia đình con bé."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:29.90,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{"You will treat Main as a noble."}"Các ngươi phải xem Myne như một quý tộc".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.71,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Those are the terms of this contract.}Đây là nội dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:43.25,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{So if I sign this contract, you \Nwon't be my little sister anymore?}Nếu kí vào nó, em sẽ không còn là em gái chị sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.55,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Mm...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.35,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{But I don't want that!}Nhưng chị không muốn thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.55,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I don't want this either,}Em cũng không muốn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.46,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{but I don't want to put you \Nin danger anymore, Tuuli.}nhưng em không thể để chị gặp nguy hiểm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.98,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Something might happen to Mom or Kamil next.}Và cả mẹ lẫn Kamil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.09,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I don't want to put my \Nfamily in danger anymore.}Em không muốn đặt gia đình mình vào nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.47,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.91,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Even if we're not family anymore...}Dù không còn là gia đình...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.91,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Even if I can't call you \Nmy big sister anymore...}Dù em không thể gọi chị nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.36,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I still want to be able \Nto see your face, Tuuli!}Thì em vẫn có thể gặp chị, Turi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:17.61,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'll keep doing my best to make picture \Nbooks and toys for you and Kamil, Tuuli.}Em sẽ cố gắng làm sách tranh cho Kamil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.49,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{So please... let me at least see you.}Nên... hãy để em gặp chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.58,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Main, please don't cry.}Myne, đừng khóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:27.17,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{I promise I'll do my best to learn how to \Nread, so I can read these books you're making.}Chị hứa sẽ cố gắng học đọc để đọc được sách em viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:31.25,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Tuuli, once you become a \Nprofessional seamstress,}Turi, khi nào chị thành thợ may chuyên nghiệp,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.39,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'll send you my clothing orders, \Nso I want you to make them.}em sẽ gửi đơn hàng đến cho chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.91,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{I promise you. I'll make you \Nall your clothes, Main.}Chị hứa với em, nhất định sẽ may cho em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I love you, Tuuli.}Em yêu chị, Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.18,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I couldn't be prouder of my older sister.}Chị gái đáng tự hào của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.41,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{Main...}Myne...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.52,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{You're leaving your parents far too early.}Con rời xa vòng tay gia đình sớm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.52,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Mom.}Con xin lỗi mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.78,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{You get sick easily, so \Nyou need to be careful.}Con dễ bệnh lắm nên cẩn thận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.48,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{Make sure you listen to everyone around you,}Hãy nghe lời mọi người,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.46,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{so you don't cause them any trouble.}đừng gây rắc rối cho ai nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.92,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{Don't go running off on your own.}Đừng tự làm gì một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.92,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{Make sure you help out when you can,}Hãy nhờ người khác giúp đỡ,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.46,Default_Top,Effa,0,0,0,,{and make sure you don't \Nrely too much on others.}và cũng đừng quá tin tưởng vào họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.11,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{I usually just listen and say, \N"Yeah, yeah," to all of this,}Mọi khi mình sẽ chỉ vâng vâng, con biết rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.92,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{but knowing I won't hear \Nthis anymore is just...}nhưng giờ sẽ không được nghe mẹ nhắc nhở nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.52,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{I love you, my dear little Main.}Mẹ yêu con, Myne bé bỏng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.60,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I love you, too, Mom.}Con cũng yêu mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.50,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Mom, do you want me to \Nwrite your name for you?}Mẹ, con viết tên hộ mẹ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.07,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{I've been practicing how to write, as well.}Mẹ gần đây cũng học viết chữ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.38,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Dad, is it okay if I hold Kamil?}Ba, con bế Kamil được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:47.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm going to be making picture books just \Nfor you, so make sure you read them, okay?}Chị sẽ làm sách cho em nên nhớ đọc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.41,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Is your arm okay, Dad?}Tay ba ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.22,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I'm fine.}Ừm, không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.97,Default,Main,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi ba, tất cả là tại con.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:03.72,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{And I'm sorry that I couldn't \Nprotect you, Main.}Ba cũng xin lỗi vì không bảo vệ được con.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:08.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No, you always protected me, Dad.}Không, ba lúc nào cũng bảo vệ con cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:13.37,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{If I ever get married, I want to marry \Nsomeone who'll protect me just like you.}Sau này có chồng, con cũng muốn\N người đó có thể bảo vệ mình như ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:17.67,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{You're just supposed to say that \Nyou want to marry me, Main.}Thế thì chỉ cần kết hôn với ba là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I want to marry you, Dad!}Con muốn thành cô dâu của ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.00,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{I've always wanted my \Ndaughter to say that to me,}Ba luôn muốn con gái mình nói thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:30.56,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{but now that my wish came true, \Nmy daughter's leaving me...}nhưng giờ giấc mơ thành sự thật thì con gái lại phải rời xa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:32.88,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{This is too much to bear.}Thật đau khổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:37.68,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{My name is going to change, and I won't \Nbe able to call you "Dad" anymore,}Tên con sẽ thay đổi và không thể gọi ba là ba nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.50,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{but I'll always be your daughter.}Nhưng con vẫn luôn là con gái ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.39,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'll protect this whole city.}Con sẽ bảo vệ thành phố này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.53,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{The whole city, eh?}Thành phố luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.77,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main, restrain yourself!}Myne, bình tĩnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.38,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No, I need to use this mana,}Không, con cần phải sử dụng nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.74,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{because it was born from the \Nlove that I have for my family.}Vì nó được sinh ra từ tình yêu của gia đình!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.09,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm going to use it for my family!}Con sẽ dùng nó cho gia đình mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.17,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main...}Myne...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.05,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The king and queen of the Gods, \Nwho rule upon the sky so high,}Vua và nữ hoàng, những người ngự trị trời cao,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{are the Gods of Darkness and \NLight, husband and wife.}thần ánh sáng, bóng tối, cùng vợ chồng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.27,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The Eternal Five that \Nrule upon this land...}Năm vị thần huyền thoại cai quản vùng đất này...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.04,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The Goddess of Water, Fruhtrane.}Nữ thần nước, Fruhtrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.00,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The God of Fire, Leidenschaft.}Thần lửa Leidenschaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.68,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The Goddess of Wind, Schutzaria.}Nữ thần gió, Schutzaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.94,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The Goddess of Earth, Geduldh.}Nữ thần đất, Geduldh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.59,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The God of Life, Ewigleben.}Thần sự sống, Ewigleben.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Hear my prayers and bless us.}Xin hãy lắng nghe và chúc phúc!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.82,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I offer you my heart.}Con cầu nguyện từ tận trái tim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.33,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I offer you my prayers and gratitude...}Con xin dâng lên lòng biết ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.80,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Please repay them with \Nyour divine protection!}Xin hãy bảo vệ họ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.20,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{This is...}Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.09,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Give us the power to heal pain.}Xin hãy chữa lành những vết thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.59,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{My wound... is all better?}Vết thương... lành lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.52,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The power to continue toward our goals.}Ban sức mạnh có thể tiến tới mục tiêu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.78,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The power to ward off evil.}Sức mạnh đẩy lùi ác quỷ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.27,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The power to endure hardship.}Sức mạnh vượt qua gian khổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.27,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Bless my loved ones with these powers.}Ban phước đến những người con yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:29.26,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{This is my last blessing to all of you.}Đây là lời chúc phúc của con.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.29,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Tuuli.}Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.89,Default,Main,0,0,0,,Kamil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.30,Default,Main,0,0,0,,Mẹ.{Mom.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.81,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Dad.}Ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.03,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Everyone...}Mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.90,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I love you.}Con yêu tất cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:19.12,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{The contract spell is now complete.}Giờ thì khế ước đã hoàn thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.13,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{The one who stands before \Nyou now is Rozemyne.}Người đứng trước các ngươi là Rozemyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.70,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{She is the daughter of an upper-class noble.}Con gái của một quý tộc cấp cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.34,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{If you'll excuse us.}Vậy tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.20,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{May you stay well and healthy.}Hãy cẩn thận chăm sóc sức khoẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.52,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Goodbye...}Tạm biệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.39,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much for coming by today.}Cảm ơn vì mọi người đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:47.34,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I pray that we get to meet again \Nfrom the bottom of my heart.}Cầu chúc chúng ta lại được gặp nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.43,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Morning, Lutz. Did something happen?}Chào cậu Lutz, có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:09.85,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{I guess Main really isn't here.}Myne không còn ở đây nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.47,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{No, Main is gone.}Ừm, Myne đi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.82,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{If you've got time to cry \Nabout it, get to work!}Còn thời gian khóc lóc thì lo làm việc đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:20.38,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{I don't care if it's Main or Rozemyne.}Ta không quan tâm Myne hay Rozenmyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:22.26,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{What does she desire more than anything?}Thứ con bé muốn là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:23.21,Default,Lutz,0,0,0,,{Books!}Sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:25.04,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Precisely!}Chính xác!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:27.31,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{There's only one thing we need to do.}Thứ duy nhất chúng ta có thể làm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:29.89,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{And that's business!}đó là buôn bán!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:34.35,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{In order to ensure she lives up to everything \Nthat being the daughter of the lord entails,}Đảm bảo cuộc sống của con bé \Nnhư một con gái của lãnh chúa,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.61,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I'll need you to guide her \Nas sternly as possible.}hãy hướng dẫn một cách nghiêm khắc nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.00,Default,Fran,0,0,0,,{As you wish.}Vâng thưa ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.34,Default,Fran,0,0,0,,{I will give this task my all.}Tôi sẽ cố gắng hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:45.03,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{I'm going to be able to make hair \Naccessories at Missus Corinna's!}Con đã có thể làm phụ kiện ở\N xưởng của tiểu thư Corinna đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:47.35,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{That must be thanks to Main's blessing.}Chắc là nhờ Myne chúc phúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.04,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{I'm home!}Ba về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:52.34,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{I ran into Gil at the square and was \Nable to find out how Main's been doing.}Tình cờ gặp Gil nên hỏi được tình hình của Myne đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:53.52,Default,Effa,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank goodness.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.59,Default,Tuuli,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and tell us, Dad!}Mau nói đi ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:04.61,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Your job will be to spread the printing business\Nas a new industry throughout this domain,}Công việc của con sẽ là phát triển ngành\Ncông nghiệp in ấn trên khu vực này.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:05.93,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,Rozemyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:07.09,Default,Rozemyne,0,0,0,,{I understand.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.51,Italics,Rozemyne,0,0,0,,{I'm going to protect everyone.}Mình sẽ bảo vệ mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:14.91,Italics,Rozemyne,0,0,0,,Để làm thế thì cần sản xuất thật nhiều sách.
